<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[لعِص]</span>: قال ابن دريد: اللَّعِص العَسِر.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
